message:
The videos of Sydney JavaScript usergroup gathering for July 2013 are now online.

Feel free to watch and share with your friends 
#SydJS
name: Videos from Sydney JavaScript UG, 17 July 2013 « GuruStop.NET (@Meligy)
caption: gurustop.net
description: Last month I started a new habit, recording SydJS usergroup videos. Although there are not so many views of these on YouTube, I got a call from a friend who can’t make it to the gathering and thinks the video are useful, so, I’m continuing with them…
